 and the age group of the family members. Moreover, all the diseases will be covered from the first day after [Ayushman Bharat Yojana Beneficiaries Registration at CSC](https://sarkariyojana.com/ayushman-bharat-yojana-beneficiaries-registration-csc-common-service-centers/).", "005-normal": "Furthermore, govt. will also provide transport allowances to the beneficiaries. All the Public / Private empanelled hospitals will get this amount directly into their account and this treatment would be cashless for all the people whose name appears in the [SECC-2011 Data](https://sarkariyojana.com/all-india-bpl-list-2018-download-secc-2011-data/)."}, "002-section": {"000-title": "References", "001-normal": "\u2014 For all other details, visit the official website pmjay.gov.in", "002-normal": "**Also Read** \u2013 [Ayushman Family Cards for Health Insurance under PMRSSM](https://sarkariyojana.com/ayushman-family-cards-health-insurance-pmrssm-modicare/)"}}